data.description: Ask about the Preferred Lender's incredible offering of up to $8,000 in lender paid closing costs! Make an incredible deal even better by buying that interest rate down! Welcome to your dream home at M West II Co where luxury meets convenience in a serene, gated community setting. This stunning 3-story end unit townhome boasts 2 bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms. The only M West II Townhome with a detached home feel due to sweeping views of the private nature preserve out every window and zero views of neighbors. As an end unit, the home enjoys an abundance of natural light throughout the year. The large fully fenced backyard, complete with low maintenance dog-friendly turf, includes a large, detached deck as the perfect space for outdoor relaxation and entertaining. Step inside to discover a thoughtfully designed open concept floor plan, where the kitchen, dining, and living areas seamlessly flow together, ideal for both everyday living and entertaining guests. The kitchen boasts modern amenities and ample counter space, while the vaulted living room is bathed in natural light from the massive floor to ceiling windows. Upstairs, the primary bedroom awaits, offering a tranquil retreat complete with a full ensuite, walk-in closet, and European-style bathroom featuring an oversized shower and soaking tub. The Juliette balcony offers more views of the nature preserve surrounding this unique property. The lower level of the home features a versatile secondary bedroom and full bathroom, perfect for guests, a home office, or an exercise room. With easy access to the outdoors and the 2-car garage, convenience is always at your fingertips. Residents of M West II enjoy a wealth of amenities, including a community pool, clubhouse, fitness center, and dog park. The 11-acre nature preserve, complete with a private walking trail, offers endless opportunities for outdoor exploration and relaxation. Residents use the private paths to quickly access Star Provisions, Mr. Coffee or Brash for their morning coffee runs. With a new PATH trail and the Beltline in development right outside the community gate, M West II will be even more easily connected to THE WORKS, Top Golf, the Silver Comet Trail, and more. Access is the key word with residents having easy access to the largest Pickle Ball facility in the city across the street, a short walk to Westside ProvisionsCO eateries and entertainment and a 5-minute drive to the new Westside Reservoir Park. Welcome to your dream home at M West II Co where luxury meets convenience in a small, gated community setting. Make this dream a reality by scheduling your private tour today! And don't forget to ask the listing team about the massive closing costs incentives available to you!
